	<title><a href="https://www.apidays.global/">API Days</a> <a href="https://www.apidays.global/helsinki_and_north/">Helsinki</a> 2025</title>
	<author>Erik Wilde, <a href="https://www.openapis.org/" title="OpenAPI Initiative">OAI</a> Ambassador</author>
	<affiliation>Principal Consultant, <a href="https://innoq.com/en/">INNOQ</a></affiliation>
